      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Binary only uses 0s and 1s. \nEach digit represents a power of 2 starting
    from the right with 1 (2^0) with each number doubling 2 (2^1), 4 (2^2) etc\n\nTo
    convert binary into a decimal multiply each digit by its positional value and
    add them together. "
